{"tid":2101575,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局：正籌辦「社區隔離中心」 位置遠離民居","createTime":"2020-07-10T02:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T02:46:05.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8b24efda251da593ca1e4986bdb16d997a7e4a","tid":2101575,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:06:45.000Z","msg":"醫管局：正籌辦社區隔離中心 位置遠離民居<br />\n發佈時間 2020-07-10 09:55<br />\n<br />\n醫管局聯網服務總監楊諦岡在一個電台節目表示，相信本港疫情會持續反覆，現時醫管局有約1200張一線隔離病床，使用率六成多，局方會隨時準備啟用約500張二線隔離病床，並在社區設隔離中心接收病情穩定和接近康復的患者，以騰空一線隔離病床予新患者。他指政府正積極籌辦隔離中心，位置會遠離民居。<br />\n<br />\n楊諦岡又指，醫管局緊急服務自5月起陸續恢復，包括電腦掃描和磁力共振，至今已恢復疫情前服務，至於預約手術和門診則恢復接近八、九成，有鑑於本港出現新一波疫情，未恢復的非緊急服務會維持暫停，局方會根據疫情檢視服務。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346357&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjm8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=ce527799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346357</a>"},{"pid":"bebf4e18016d5de3b6ce273fdb2b2c666f0338dd","tid":2101575,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:07:25.000Z","msg":"東平洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d190ddd4fdaafb24811851ddbc127aaa0beacee9","tid":2101575,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17b166d414851af5232efc0b36d0a26effe06a3","tid":2101575,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"黃絲隔離中心"},{"pid":"ebaf651fac53fde0734df49fe5e18d96ec03dbf2","tid":2101575,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:09:14.000Z","msg":"同起精神病康復中心一樣<br />\n過到地區果關先算<img src=\"/assets/face